{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were in these wagons three days and three nights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived at a place-- stopped at a place on the 10th of October, very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We looked through the little window up there, and we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] saw a sign at the railway station, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then there was another sign, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we said, oh, we are in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It looks like Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It looks like Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe here we-- we're going to start working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The platform of the train was floodlit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we saw loads of SS men with dogs and whips and, you know, on-- on the platform.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we also saw some people in a striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The doors were opened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the SS men were shouting, raus!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were put into-- in front of each wagon in row of fives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They selected men, women, and children to go to one side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, one loud speaker called out and said, look here, we are going to the camp, all of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You are going to work for the German Reich, all of you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're going to take the women, children, and the old people by bus to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you-- the people who can walk, the young men, young men who can walk, will walk to the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's approximately a half an hour of-- of walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one woman, who begged an SS man to-- not to be-- she said, I'm young.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I can walk with my husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
